8d" id="_83233f16-74f6-4d59-9dcf-f543d73f41fa" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> and ventilation <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_e99d4f04-90f9-4d5f-8715-1632978714f9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref>; or</li></ol></li><li id="_254bc8d0-7279-4f63-8521-97c3c05a9a56">Part H6 in NCC Volume Two and Section 10 and Section 13 of the ABCB Housing Provisions, the parts of a building’s <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1269_0.5.0.xml#_13553d4f-118c-47e2-90ba-9892194abdf6" id="_23542057-0c9c-41d6-84a6-e725f43c9a06" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">fabric</xref> that separate artificially heated or cooled spaces from—<ol><li>the exterior of the building; or</li><li>other spaces that are not artificially heated or cooled.</li></ol></li></ol></glossdef></abcb-glossentry>